data.description: Discover your dream home in Royse City, TX, with this impeccable 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence. Step inside to find an inviting open-concept layout, seamlessly connecting the eat-in kitchen, complete with electric range and dual sinks, to the spacious dining area and large living room. The primary suite offers a peaceful escape with a walk-in closet and a luxurious ensuite bath featuring quartz counters and a walk-in shower. Throughout the home, enjoy the elegance of luxury vinyl flooring and the convenience of Vivint smart home features. Outside, this property impresses with a well-maintained sprinkler system, an extended concrete patio with a covered back patio deck, an 8x8 storage shed for organization, a thriving garden, and energy-efficient solar panels!! This home is not just a residence; it's a modern oasis designed for comfort, style, and located within the desirable Royse City ISD! Experience the perfect blend of luxury and practicality in this home and make it yours today!!
